Package cetus.analysis

Class PointsToRel

  • java.lang.Object
    • cetus.analysis.PointsToRel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable
    public class PointsToRel
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    Points to relationships represent the link from the head of the relationship to the tail. The head is the pointer variable/symbol and the tail is the variable/location/ symbol being pointed to. The relationship can be definite or possible.
